{
  "stem": "21319.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't-- so many things happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the day when they-- they-- was in-- in-- in-- in Vivikond, they liquidated Vivikond seven weeks later, and they took us all to Vaivara, to the other camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Was very, very tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I remember that in Vivikond and in Vaivara, they did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They used to take-- if a man was sick-- because a lot of people were sick from the typhus and all that, the dysentery-- and couldn't go to work with the group, he used to order a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Used to order his-- his helpers to take the man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They used to throw him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Around Vivikond, there were [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, because it was swamp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The area was very swampy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So they had around the camp large one, like from here to here, dug-- how do you dig it-- hole around the camp so the water would start run in this-- I don't know what-- what do you call this.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, in German, used to say [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I don't-- anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So they used to take any man, anybody who was left after the [GERMAN], after-- to-- who didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They used to go in the barrack and check them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I was at that time watching-- was-- over the children's barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So they didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Things which come back to my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But they used to find the man, if a man was staying, they found him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They used to bring him to the-- to this big holes, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Tell him to take off his clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then drop him in this swampy water.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
